<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>일기 수정 - 감정 일기</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=SUIT:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'SUIT', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fef6f0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        main {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #444;
        }
        input[type="text"],
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.7rem;
            background-color: #ffc1a1;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ffa577;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
    <h2>일기 수정하기</h2>
    <form action="/diary/{{diary.diaryId}}/edit" method="post">
        <input type="text" name="title" value="{{diary.title}}" placeholder="제목">
        <textarea name="content" placeholder="내용">{{diary.content}}</textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn">수정 완료</button>
    </form>
</main>
</body>
</html>
